Kestrel (20), Peregrine Falcon (1), Black Phoebe (15),
Vermilion Flycatcher (1 – a female at Riverview Cemetery inBrawley), Ash-throated Flycatcher (3), Western Kingbird
(25), Loggerhead Shrike (5), Common Raven (2), Tree Swallow
(5), Northern Rough-winged Swallow (2), Cliff Swallow
(150), Barn Swallow (6 – six at the intersection of Carter
and Fites Roads southwest of Brawley were likely adults
